social_posts.post_text: Honestly she would’ve cried if it was anyone but me. #mamasgirl
It’s the coziest time of the year. ♥️🌲

So we went to @legolandcalifornia for the first time ever and I didn’t know what to expect at all. Let me tell you, we all had so much fun!! Every one of us keeps saying how much we want to go back. There is so much to do and we didn’t get to cover it all and we just had so much fun! It is perfect for Tennessee’s age but Lux had a great time too. Highly recommend if you have little ones. #LEGOLANDCalifornia
#HolidaysatLEGOLAND #BuildandRaceLLC #sponsored

we had so much fun at @knottsberryfarm. I hadn’t been in about 20 years. It’s so much fun getting to experience things with kids because it’s a completely new experience. Both girls absolutely loved it. Poor lux is scared of the characters but she still had a great time. Where should our next adventure be??

She is in her dress era right now. 

All dresses :@aliceandames
(They just restocked all their most popular prints. We’ve been wearing these dresses since Tennessee was really little. We love them.)
Happy New year everyone ! Here’s to a great year. I’m so thankful for this tiny community. ♥️

We have no photos together and I wanted a cute one for today. I asked Tennessee and a stranger to take some for us and these are the best we got. …I know we all know it’s dumb. The cheesy my spouse is the greatest posts on their birthday or your anniversary. BUT it’s my 10 YEAR wedding anniversary. When I was younger I thought that to be married 10 years was like ..you OOOOLD. but now here we are. I’m truly so lucky to have found this guy. He really is the greatest. All the things he has done and helped me with or been there for.  He is my everything. I use to be an independent woman but now I prefer to depend on him for everything forever. Haha. ♥️♥️♥️♥️♥️♥️

We got invited to @legolandcalifornia for their opening weekend of #NINJAGOWeekends and we had so much fun. We are big fans of Legoland already and I’ll be honest my two girls don’t watch a lot of ninja stuff so we didn’t know what to expect but even if you’re not super familiar with ninjago I promise you will still have fun! There was a scavenger hunt and ninja yoga, ninja class, we go to meet the ninjas and there’s a whole new Ninjago playground. Definitely check it out if you can. It’s every weekend through 2/20. #LEGOLANDCalifornia #sponsored

I never really thought about teaching my kids sign language but now it’s all she does. 

Our @lovevery box came with this book and she took to it so quickly. It’s really helped cut out some of the frustrations of not being able to communicate. 10/10 would recommend. 
#lovevery #loveverygift

Its official these girls love it here. We were invited to the 5th annual peanut’s celebration at @knottsberryfarm and truly had the most fun ever. It’s going on every day now through February 26. The peanuts gang are taking over the park with fun stuff to do throughout. There is a new show, fun games for the kids to play, fun photo ops, a space theme exhibit with a snoopy meet and greet and pigpen even bought out baby piglets and so much more. We can’t wait to go back. 🥜 #knottspeanutscelebration #knottsberryfarm

I somehow got invited to @knottsberryfarm media event for the boysenberry festival and had so much fun. It was 21 and older so I went with my girlfriend Kristina while dom stayed home with the children. It was weird being out with a friend I felt like we should smoke cigarettes and use profanity and I don’t even smoke cigarettes or use profanity. lol. The boysenberry festival is March 10 through April 16. Make sure to try out the new eats and say hi if you see me. ♥️

Tennessee and I got invited to the @nickelodeon Kid’s Choice Awards and seriously had the most fun ever. She got her hair nails and makeup done before the show and felt like a princess! Her favorite part of the awards was screaming all night and watching everyone get slimed! Her only disappointment was that bubble guppies didn’t perform. 😹 #KCA #nickfamilyinsiders #nickelodeon #nickjr  #momlife #girlmom #grwm
RNOAF! : @ithacahummus Kalamata olive hummus. 🫒

It’s time for a new @barkbox !! March’s box theme is sponge Bob 🧽 and the toys are looking extra cute! Kenya can be a little picky with toys but she always loves her BarkBox toys. Make sure to grab one before they’re gone. ♥️
We don’t drink soda so this is the first time my girls have ever tried it. Tbh I hated it too. lol
Real conversations with a 4 year old part one.
Unboxing for @nickelodeon ‘s new show bossy bear. #nickfamilyinsiders #nickelodeon #nickjr #bossybear #unboxing #family #momlife #girlmom #karaoke #funnykids
My sister in law has pet chickens so I don’t have to.
Who can relate??
Just found this pic of Lux’s first time at Disneyland and decided it needed a spot on the feed. I love these little rascals.
Asking my 4 year old if she knows what st. Patrick’s day is.

It has been so fun getting to experience Knott’s with the girls. It’s safe to say we are now big fans of Knott’s and Snoopy. I will say out of all the times we’ve been now the boysenberry festival was our favorite. Everyone is so into it and there’s so much food, it’s just a really fun experience. The girls loved tasting a bunch of the food! Tennessee was trying to make RNOAF for all of them. Haha. But honestly if you have been wanting go to Knott’s or have a pass you definitely need to go for the festival. It goes on until April 16 and make sure you buy a tasting card it’s 💯worth it. @knottsberryfarm

We got invited to see a sneak peak of the 100th episode of @pawpatrol and it did not disappoint. I know you all love paw patrol as much as we do so you know this was a dream come true for the girls. Thanks @nickelodeon and @spinmaster for a magical day.

Working on our animal sounds. 🥹

#LoveveryGift #Lovevery @Lovevery

Reviews No One Asked For: @mayascookiessandiego 
Today Tennessee is reviewing Maya’s newest cookie collection: the cake collection. Red velvet was Tennessee’s favorite and let me tell you it is SPOT ON. If you like red velvet cake but want it magically transformed into a cookie this is for you. Lemon Bundt cake was my favorite but holy moly all three are to die for honestly. Maya’s cookies are all vegan and they have gf options as well, our whole family will agree that they are the superior cookie. They graciously gave us a discount to share with you all, use code: DANIBRI10 for $ off. This is not an ad, I just absolutely love supporting small companies we love, especially ones owned by a boss lady! 💪🏼 🍪
Parents of little nappers, who can relate? We all know what happens when it stops. 😬
If you’ve never checked out miniland at @legolandcalifornia now is the time! Construction of San Diego is now complete and pretty spectacular to see!

We took the girls to their first movie at the theater! We saw Mario and both girls loved it. lol. Lux was so good she just sat on my lap and enjoyed the show from start to finish.  She also can’t decide if she doesn’t like Bowser or if he’s her favorite 😹
And for all you mom shamers dying to tell me how dangerous popcorn is for littles; no, Lux does not eat popcorn.

It’s almost summer time and soak city is open! It was all of our first time and we had such a fun day! These girls love water and there was a huge section for littles and honestly lots to do for every age. The entire day Tennessee was already asking to go back. 💦

Summer is here .. even though it’s still spring. lol. Fiesta Village just opened up at @knottsberryfarm and it did not disappoint. More rides, new shows, and the summer tasting card we’re all so much fun! Tbh knotts never disappoints. 

#GhostTownAlive #KnottsSummerNights #KnottsFiestaVillage

Okay, now let’s go play the lotto.
RNOAF : @oat.haus chocolate birthday cake.

@garfield is celebrating his 45th birthday this year and @nickelodeon sent us the best package to help celebrate. The girls are now obsessed with Garfield and Odie! It’s so fun when things from my childhood come back so the girls can enjoy it too. 
#nickelodeon #nickjr #garfield #garfield45 #nickfamilyinsiders
Last week we got together with all the girl’s cousins and got to throw a Paw Patrol snow cone party! I think it finally feels like summer.  @nickelodeon @pawpatrol #nickfamilyinsiders @nickjr

Still here. I can’t believe summer is almost over (the break not the season). This would normally make me thrilled but Tennessee is going to be starting Kindergarten in a few short weeks and my mom heart is so sad. But.. it’s almost August so we will be going all out for our birthday month but that’s nothing new. Anyone have kids going to school for the time this year?

Mom and Dad. 🩷 
We had the best night ever last night. I didn’t watch anyone’s stories of Taylor for the entire tour because I didn’t want to ruin the surprise of seeing it for the first time. lolol. Seriously one of the best concerts of all time but more importantly it was the FIRST date @dominic.phillip and I had since Tennessee was born almost  FIVE YEARS AGO! It was so strange being able to talk for so long without being interrupted. Also iso a babysitter so we can do it again. lol ♥️♥️♥️
POV: after you put the kids to sleep every night you make friendship bracelets for the Eras Tour.

This summer is really flying by! One of the most fun things we’ve done this summer was definitely going to @skyparksantasvillage ! I hadn’t been there in so long I didn’t know what to expect but they really outdid our expectations! I definitely want to go back for the holidays. ♥️ 
@skyparkbikepark

Hold on to the memories they will hold on to you. 🎶 ✨ 
When your gf says let’s go at 5pm you start getting ready and you do as your told. Best. Night. Ever. ♥️

First day of kinder. First day ever leaving her anywhere without her family. Big day for all of us here. She was super nervous of the unknown but we snuck in to class early so she was the first student and got to talk to her teacher and give her a little gift and she told me “I’m not nervous anymore” ♥️

If you are looking for some Halloween fun for the kids, you need to check out LEGOLAND’s Brick or Treat celebration!! The girls absolutely loved it. Lux gets really spooked if anything is very scary at all and this was perfect. It was set up so cute with so many shows and brick or treat stations for candy. All the Halloween festivities start at 3 so make sure you plan accordingly and have fun! 👻 🎃 #legolandcalifornia #sponsored
Every time.
October first. Family + pumpkins seemed on brand.

Is there anything better than little voices?? 🥹 

@lovevery #gifted

We recently got to check out Knotts Spooky Farm with the girls so I put together a list of five fun things to do while you’re there. We all had so much fun it’s perfect for little ones, nothing scary at all. @knottsberryfarm #knottsspookyfarm

@nickelodeon invited us to a halloween party at the animation building ! The girls are obsessed with @officialpeppa so they were two peppa pigs. There was food and treats, pumpkin decorating, slime making, the girls tried cotton candy for the first time ever 😅 and we even got the girls drawn by artists from the Loud House. 10/10 Best Halloween party ever.
Two black cats. 🐈‍⬛ 🌙

My littlest baby is TWO. She lights up every room she’s in. This girl is smart and polite, she is kind, she loves to make everyone laugh and she will always make you feel good inside. She’s also tough and won’t let anyone push her around. The perfect completion to our family. She has my whole heart. Happy Birthday to my little queen. 👑

We just went to @knottsberryfarm for the holidays and it did not disappoint. Not joking the snoopy on ice show alone was worth it. It was soooo good!! The girls loved every minute. Add this to your list of things to do this holiday. ♥️🎄 
#knottsberryfarm #knottsmerryfarm #snoopy

If you’re looking for something fun to do this weekend and you’re local you should check out Holidays at @legolandcalifornia . We had so much fun! It’s going on through January 7. 

#legolandcalifornia #LEGOland

#Ad The holidays are our favorite time of the year and I’m always trying to find new ways to make memories with my girls. We are always running around doing things so I thought it would be fun to decorate their bunk bed, get out some treats and have a movie night. The girls loved PAW Patrol: The Mighty Movie so much and have been asking to watch it again so I knew it would be the perfect movie to cuddle up to and of course kids never want the night to end so we did a double feature with Baby Shark’s Big Movie! Both movies are now streaming on @ParamountPlus so make sure to go watch and start your holidays making new memories with Nickelodeon. 
@Nickelodeon @NickelodeonFamily @ParamountPlus
Wishing you all a Merry Christmas🎄♥️ ✝️
